text: Arne Jacobsen is an archer from Denmark. He was born on 12 June 1942. Jacobsen competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1976 Summer Olympics.Arne JacobsenArne Erik JACOBSEN == References == Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Danish archers Category:Olympians for Denmark Category:People from Aarhus
